blog.name: sittingthere-bythewater
blog.title: you've ruined my life by not being mine
blog.description:
afie//26//swifts creek
living my dream job in rural victoria
speak now taylor is my jam
firefighter with itchy feet
hopeless romantic

rep tour perth AND melbourne 😍

summary: Two years ago I applied for a seasonal position in my dream job...in a different state! Literally only looked up the Swifts...
body:
Two years ago I applied for a seasonal position in my dream job…in a different state! Literally only looked up the Swifts Creek depot because it had the word Swifts in it.

So I picked up my life and moved 4000km’s across the country, to a town of 300 where I knew nobody.

It has now been exactly one year since I moved here, and today during the second month of my second fire season, I had the best career day of my life. Never been so happy.

Firefighting and Aviation are my childhood dream jobs, and today I got to live out both. So stoked🤙🏻🤙🏻
